name: GU Roctane Lemonade Gel
description: This gel shot contains an amino acid blend designed to provide nutritional support for extended sessions and endurance sports. The Roctane blend is fuel for activities that require focus, concentration and sustained mental acuity.Ingredients: Matodextrin, water, fructose, ornithine alpha-ketoglutarate (okg), histidine, leucine, sodium citrate, valine, sea salt, citric acid, potassium citrate, calcium carbonate, natural flavor, tartaric acid, isoleucine, malic acid, gellan gum, sodium benzoate (preservative), potassium sorbate (preservative), D-alpha-tocopheryl acetate (natural vitamin E).
